name: Manulife Multifactor Developed International Index ETF
longDescription: In regard to the Unhedged Units, the Fund seeks to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses, the performance of the John Hancock Dimensional Developed International Index (CAD) (the Index). In regard to the Hedged Units, the Fund seeks to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible and before fees and expenses, the performance of the John Hancock Dimensional Developed International Index (CAD Hedged) (the CAD Hedged Index). The Fund invests directly or indirectly primarily in equity securities of issuers from developed markets outside of the U.S. and Canada.
